	<description><![CDATA[
		<p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><strong><img style='margin-right: 5px; float: left;' alt='fwgallery_content_plugin_box' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/box.png ' height='171' width='130' /></strong></span></p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><strong>FW Gallery Content Plugin</strong></span></p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><strong><br /></strong></span></p><div><span style='font-size: 8pt;'><strong>Compatibility: </strong>Joomla 3.0</span></div><div><span style='font-size: 8pt;'><strong>License: </strong>GNU/GPL</span></div><div><span style='font-size: 8pt;'><strong>Current version: </strong>1.5.0</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><span style='font-size: 8pt;'>FW  Gallery Content plugin allows you to insert images in your article and to turn your texts into real masterpieces. </span><br /></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'>FW Gallery Content Plugin has been installed successfully and now you can apply it to your FW Gallery!</span></p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'>Thank you for your choice! We hope you will enjoy Fastw3b extensions!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>How to use:</strong></p><ol><li>Go to Components &gt;&gt; FW Gallery &gt;&gt; Plugins and enable the plugin.</li><li>Choose the place in the article where you would like to insert the image.</li><li>Choose the image and type in the chosen place of the article: {fwgallery id:36}, where id:36 is an image id number.</li></ol><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><strong>Here are some useful links for you:</strong></span></p><div><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/joomla-extensions/product/6-fw-gallery-comment.html'><img style='float: left;' alt='bullet-green' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/bullet-green.png' height='20' width='20' /></a><a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/joomla-extensions/product/12-fw-gallery-content-plugin.html'>How-to-use guide &gt;&gt;</a></span></p></div><div><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/contact-us.html'><img style='float: left;' alt='bullet-green' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/bullet-green.png' height='20' width='20' />Contact us &gt;&gt;</a></span></p></div><div><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/forum/index.php?board=126.0'><img style='float: left;' alt='bullet-green' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/bullet-green.png' height='20' width='20' /></a><a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/forum/index.php?board=84.0'>Suggest your idea &gt;&gt;</a></span></p></div><div><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><a target='_blank' href='http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension-specific/fw-gallery-extensions/14024'><img style='float: left;' alt='bullet-green' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/bullet-green.png' height='20' width='20' /></a><a target='_blank' href='http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension-specific/fw-gallery-extensions/13352'>View JED reviews &gt;&gt;</a></span></p></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><img style='margin-right: 10px; float: left;' alt='icon_info' src='../plugins/content/fwgallery/fwgallery/assets/images/icon_info.png' height='50' width='50' />If you have any questions, feel free to <a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/forum/index.php?board=84.0'>contact us</a> and get professional support!</span></p><div><span style='font-size: 10pt;'>Follow us on <a target='_blank' href='http://twitter.com/#%21/Fastw3b'>Twitter</a> and <a target='_blank' href='http://www.facebook.com/pages/edit/?id=165610930146118&amp;sk=basic#%21/pages/Fastw3b/165610930146118'>Facebook</a> to be informed about <a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/joomla-extensions/product/7-fw-gallery.html'>FW Gallery</a> latest news!</span></div><div><span style='font-size: 10pt;'> </span></div><div><span style='font-size: 10pt;'> </span></div><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'><br /></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-size: 10pt;'>Developed by <a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/'>Fastw3b</a></span></p><div><span style='font-size: 10pt;'>Copyright &copy; 2007 - 2013 <a target='_blank' href='http://fastw3b.net/'>Fastw3b</a></span></div>	
	]]></description>
	<files>
		<filename plugin="fwgallery">fwgallery.php</filename>
		<folder>fwgallery</folder>
	</files>
	<config>
		<fields name="params">
			<fieldset name="basic">
				<field name="image_box_width" type="text" default="220" label="Image Box Width" description="" />
				<field name="image_box_height" type="text" default="220" label="Image Box Height" description="" />
				<field name="align" type="radio" default="left" label="Image align" description="">
					<option value="left">Left</option>
					<option value="right">Right</option>
				</field>
				<field name="hide_mignifier" type="radio" default="0" label="Hide mignifier (lightbox effect)" description="">
					<option value="0">No</option>
					<option value="1">Yes</option>
				</field>
				<field name="display_name_image" type="radio" default="1" label="Display image name" description="">
					<option value="0">No</option>
					<option value="1">Yes</option>
				</field>
				<field name="display_date_image" type="radio" default="1" label="Display image date" description="">
					<option value="0">No</option>
					<option value="1">Yes</option>
				</field>
				<field name="display_owner_image" type="radio" default="1" label="Display image owner" description="">
					<option value="0">No</option>
					<option value="1">Yes</option>
				</field>
				<field name="use_voting" type="radio" default="1" label="Use Voting" description="">
					<option value="0">No</option>
					<option value="1">Yes</option>
				</field>
			</fieldset>
		</fields>
	</config>
</extension>
